# Luxanvoryx Feature Requirements

## Caffeine Tracker
- Track daily caffeine intake with visual progress indicator
- Calculate metabolism rate and estimated clearance time
- Record different beverage types with predefined caffeine content
- Display history of consumed beverages
- Show safe daily limit (400mg) and current status
- Allow adding custom beverages

## Coupon Manager
- Organize coupons by categories (dining, shopping, travel)
- Display expiration dates with visual indicators
- Sort coupons by expiry date (soonest first)
- Allow adding new coupons with category, title, and expiry date
- Provide expiry notifications for soon-to-expire coupons
- Support coupon deletion and marking as used

## Color Generator
- Interactive HSL color adjustment with sliders
- Visual representation of selected color
- Generate complementary color schemes
- Save favorite color schemes
- Random color scheme generation
- Export color values in different formats (HSL, RGB, HEX)

## General Requirements
- Intuitive and visually appealing UI with dark theme
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Persistent data storage across app restarts
- Responsive design for different screen sizes
